Polymetal Climbs 4th Day This Week as Gold and Silver Advance

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-09-02T07:15:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-02/polymetal-climbs-4th-day-this-week-as-gold-and-silver-advance.html
OAO Polymetal, a Russian gold and
silver producer, advanced for the fourth day this week as the
price of both metals increased.  The stock jumped as much as 2.7 percent at the start of
trading and was 0.5 percent stronger at 619.8 rubles by 11:01
a.m. in Moscow.  Immediate-delivery gold gained 0.6 percent to $1,836.93 an
ounce. Spot silver rose 0.4 percent to $41.77 an ounce.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jason Corcoran at 
